{"tid":1955964,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法國首次公布最少884名長者在護老院因武漢肺炎不治","createTime":"2020-04-03T00:17:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T01:26:03.000Z","uid":130626,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"705686a6dcec19d4a6b3ca3df4ea9dd0e7a96803","tid":1955964,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T00:17:29.000Z","msg":"法國當局首次公布在護老院感染武漢肺炎死亡的人數，初步點算有最少884名長者死亡，連同過去一日在醫院新增的471宗死亡病例，自疫情爆發以來累計5387人不治，確診人數增至59100多人。<br />\n<br />\n法國自上月17日起處於封鎖狀態，民眾如非必要禁止外出。被問到疫情是否有紓緩跡象，衛生部門說，目前判斷為時尚早，強調必須小心。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1518553-20200403.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1518553-20200403.htm&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMjvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=3a75101d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1518553-20200403.htm&h=1042e3dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1518553-20200403.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f4bdcf65a1e5c9d3ba55633349313ef9f86b9327","tid":1955964,"uid":8014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T00:19:02.000Z","msg":"香港都係咁就好了 廢老票倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2296469006ffdfa7eac312b3e377344bec4b4c3","tid":1955964,"uid":37596,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T00:20:10.000Z","msg":"解決老人問題,禁足令又迫人扑野生育,歐豬又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f650b7967bcb28d8329ca15d418cf7939acc948","tid":1955964,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T00:20:21.000Z","msg":"武肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60bb93100be39e278d753f165d61d9fe69c96270","tid":1955964,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T00:57:52.000Z","msg":"唔怪得由得肺炎爆"},{"pid":"a809316e7d4063d9517f91993e2829c9d0475d